  "response": "Determining the \"best\" bulk SMS service provider can depend on specific needs like pricing, reliability, user interface, customer service, and additional features. However, some popular bulk SMS service providers in Bangladesh include:\n\n1. **SMSHorizon Bangladesh**: Known for reliability and competitive pricing.\n2. **CoreSMS**: Offers a range of messaging services with good delivery rates.\n3. **BanglaPhone**: Provides comprehensive bulk SMS services and has been around for years.\n4. **Mobireach**: Known for robust infrastructure and good customer support.\n5. **DhakaSMS**: Provides various plans suited for different scales of business operations.\n\nTo choose the best one for your needs, you may want to consider user reviews, trial their services, and compare their features and prices.",
